/// glassfish ///
- create topic or queue with name defined in RestServices bean

//////////////////

/// install activeMQ ///

- install activemq connector, follow: 
http://geertschuring.wordpress.com/2012/04/20/how-to-connect-glassfish-3-to-activemq-5/

////////////////////////


/// libVirt lib ///
- if have problem with libVirt, make sure native lib 
is accessible in /usr/lib/libVirt.so (make a symbolic link if nessesary)
- have jna.jar lib (defined in pom.xml)

///////////////////////